{"tid":1359622,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"小巴西龜個殼變白","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T06:46:21.000Z","uid":288039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ba607f2169c025b580a3edc84c55de57649308","tid":1359622,"uid":288039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"養左呢隻巴西龜仔差唔多半年<br />\n都幾活躍又會食好多野<br />\n望落好健康<br />\n但個殼不停變白<br />\n有無巴絲可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ViHQcij.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViHQcij.png&h=7ae81b4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34cf5ad435210bea364938a7e39a615634638fff","tid":1359622,"uid":282984,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"試下曬多D太陽"},{"pid":"0d523f7ca1a1bc2892efed29d116efedafcbf6d8","tid":1359622,"uid":60185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:27.000Z","msg":"唔夠太陽導致角質化 曬多啲太陽啦"},{"pid":"14223af3430c1a9a5f1dc7183e10632546c05ddb","tid":1359622,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"勤換水曬多D太陽, 食D鈣質豐富既食物"},{"pid":"ad82bf67e6bc1e4ab2a530f4b46d0f6bc27e8978","tid":1359622,"uid":209050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"佢個殼摸落去係咪有少少滑？"},{"pid":"390c3e5da74b4d7ee53b3ab0d7effa31849a2f1e","tid":1359622,"uid":209050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"日日都要曬太陽<br />\n用牙刷細細力幫佢擦吓個殼(去角質)<br />\n日日都要換水<br />\n<br />\n而家有兩個可能性<br />\n一係佢個殼上面有菌<br />\n應該係冇成日換水<br />\n如果佢個殼摸落去係有少少滑<br />\n你要去爬蟲類店 買去真菌藥膏<br />\n<br />\n第二個可能性就係有過多角質<br />\n要幫佢清潔下個殻<br />\n日日都要曬太陽"},{"pid":"60601224440ba64136fda8abff065c3412242af3","tid":1359622,"uid":288039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390c3e5da74b4d7ee53b3ab0d7effa31849a2f1e","tid":1359622,"uid":209050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"日日都要曬太陽<br />\n用牙刷細細力幫佢擦吓個殼(去角質)<br />\n日日都要換水<br />\n<br />\n而家有兩個可能性<br />\n一係佢個殼上面有菌<br />\n應該係冇成日換水<br />\n如果佢個殼摸落去係有少少滑<br />\n你要去爬蟲類店 買去真菌藥膏<br />\n<br />\n第二個可能性就係有過多角質<br />\n要幫佢清潔下個殻<br />\n日日都要曬太陽"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"有架 我差唔多日日都換<br />\n見到有屎同水變黃色就會換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我放係陽台<br />\n不過唔係成日有太陽曬到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n絲打有無真菌藥膏推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e89403897be12dfbd1e82d2f26b1e6b2450fce","tid":1359622,"uid":288039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14223af3430c1a9a5f1dc7183e10632546c05ddb","tid":1359622,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"勤換水曬多D太陽, 食D鈣質豐富既食物"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"餵開普通龜糧咋⋯<br />\n有可以餵佢食咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d19bd0798f1f82c67ff3ab049ca3c859054cf9","tid":1359622,"uid":136151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63e89403897be12dfbd1e82d2f26b1e6b2450fce","tid":1359622,"uid":288039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14223af3430c1a9a5f1dc7183e10632546c05ddb","tid":1359622,"uid":279810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"勤換水曬多D太陽, 食D鈣質豐富既食物"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"餵開普通龜糧咋⋯<br />\n有可以餵佢食咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/asse